  <main>
    <h1>About EcoBloom Florals</h1>
    <p>
      Founded in 2005 in Johannesburg, EcoBloom Florals is a sustainable floral studio passionate about
      creating beautiful arrangements while supporting local eco-friendly farms. Our mission is simple: 
      to deliver memorable floral experiences while promoting sustainable practices in the floral industry.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Sustainability Commitment</h2>
    <p>
      We source all our flowers from local eco-friendly farms that practice organic farming methods,
      reducing our carbon footprint and supporting the local economy. Our packaging is 100% biodegradable
      or recyclable, and we use natural pest control methods in our studio garden.
    </p>

